In the afternoon, I also studied `utils/attendanceUtils/leaveDayUtils.js` which provides helpers for checking whether a given day is a leave day for an employee. These helpers are used both in the attendance finalization job (to mark leave days correctly) and in the regularization controller (to prevent submitting corrections for days that are approved leave days — there's no need to correct a punch record for a day you were officially on leave).

