- Understood the non-fatal pattern: wrap signature calls in try/catch so failures don't block core flows
- Learned the `existingDriveFileId` reuse pattern to avoid double uploads in the candidate application flow
- Understood that `SignatureCredentials` acts as a universal viewer deployable at any point in the HR portal

## Challenges & Solutions
The offer letter response page is a public page (no HR auth), so the `recordOnboardingSignature` helper needed to resolve the employee's Drive folder using `emp_code` from the URL token rather than `req.user`. I updated the helper to accept an explicit `employee` document parameter instead of relying on `req.user`.

